The renewable energy mix in Germany shows a certain diversity with respect to type and location of sources. This leads to a more balanced and more continuous generation pattern. Available real data show that the simultaneously maximum available power of renewable energy sources Pmax is equivalent to about 50% of installed capacity Pinst [3, 4]:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
